               <msContents>
                  <summary>Photocopy of Commentary on Qerǝlos, ትርጓሜ: ቄርሎስ:</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="305v" facs="002">Fols 1r–305v</locus><title>Commentary on Qerǝlos, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ትርጓሜ: ቄርሎስ:</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ነገር፡ ዘጸሐፈ፡ ቄርሎስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘእለ፡ እስክንድርያ፡ ለቴዎዶስዮስ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ታኢርክ፡ ቄርሎስ፡ ማለት፡ ኃያል፡ ኅሩይ፡ ማለት፡ ነው። ወይጼወዉ፡ ቄረ፡ ሕዝቦሙ፡ ለሶርያ፡ እንዲል፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>Photocopy of Commentary on Qerǝlos, dealing with the subjects “On the Orthodox Faith,” and “The Beauty of the News.”</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
